q 0.5 G 1 w 72 718 m 540 718 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 695 Td (ACTIVE LISTENING means:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 679 Td (  - Put down your phone) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 663 Td (  - Make eye contact) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 647 Td (  - Don't formulate your response while they talk) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 631 Td (  - Reflect back: 'What I hear you saying is...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 615 Td (  - Ask: 'Did I understand that correctly?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 599 Td (  - Validate: 'That makes sense that you'd feel that way') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 583 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 567 Td (LISTENING KILLERS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 551 Td (  - Defending yourself before they finish) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 535 Td (  - Minimizing: 'It's not that bad') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 519 Td (  - Problem-solving before they ask for solutions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 503 Td (  - Bringing up your own issue in response) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 487 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 471 Td (Practice: Take turns sharing for 3 minutes each.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 455 Td (The listener can ONLY reflect back. No responding.) Tj ET

endstream
